	a <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Action> .
<urn:uuid:019cffdc-b1c5-79c3-9c4a-952ad4514ccc> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasCompletedDateTime> "2026-03-18T16:23:00-07:00"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> ;
	<https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001868> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Completed> ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "when --charter X returns zero plans, tell the user what was actually resolved and why nothing matched: e.g. 'resolved charter to Build the ClearHead Platform (explicit, README.md), graph name: build_clearhead, SPARQL returned 0 results'. silent empty with exit 0 is the worst failure mode for a query system" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "improve empty result messages for charter queries" ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasUUID> "019cffdc-b1c5-79c3-9c4a-952ad4514ccc" ;
	a <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Action> .
<urn:uuid:019cffdc-b1be-7ea3-a056-51ae79a826d9> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasCompletedDateTime> "2026-03-18T16:23:00-07:00"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> ;
	<https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001868> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Completed> ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "clearhead show graph [--charter X] dumps the actual RDF triples for a charter or the whole workspace. critical for verifying hasSubCharter triples exist and point to the right URIs — was completely blind on this during the recursive charter fix" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "add graph inspection command" ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasUUID> "019cffdc-b1be-7ea3-a056-51ae79a826d9" ;
	a <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Action> .
<urn:uuid:019cffdc-b1b8-7e63-a96f-10d0816b25ac> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasCompletedDateTime> "2026-03-18T16:17:00-07:00"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> ;
	<https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001868> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Completed> ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "clearhead query sparql '<query>' runs the query against the live workspace RDF graph and returns results. the graph infrastructure already exists — this is mostly wiring run_workspace_sql_query to a new subcommand. would have cut the recursive-charter debug session from hours to minutes" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "add sparql query command to CLI" ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasUUID> "019cffdc-b1b8-7e63-a96f-10d0816b25ac" ;
	a <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Action> .
<urn:uuid:8e798316-ed1f-512c-91d3-d02eceb47c48> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000051> <urn:uuid:019cffdc-b1ce-7842-bbf6-27f3b36feef4> , <urn:uuid:019cffdc-b1c5-79c3-9c4a-952ad4514ccc> , <urn:uuid:019cffdc-b1be-7ea3-a056-51ae79a826d9> , <urn:uuid:019cffdc-b1b8-7e63-a96f-10d0816b25ac> .
<urn:uuid:344f2a0d-1a93-537a-b42b-a0cd1b6c7760> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasSubCharter> <urn:uuid:8e798316-ed1f-512c-91d3-d02eceb47c48> .
<urn:uuid:8e798316-ed1f-512c-91d3-d02eceb47c48> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasCharterState> "Closed" ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasAlias> "observability" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Right now debugging the clearhead system requires `RUST_LOG=debug` and reading source code — you can't inspect what the graph actually contains, why a SPARQL query returned nothing, or what the system resolved a charter name to.\n\nThe architecture already has everything needed to fix this: the RDF store is queryable, the domain model is structured, and the CLI is the right place to expose it. The goal is to make the system self-describing so that bugs like the \"recursive charter returns empty\" class can be diagnosed in seconds, not hours.\n\nLonger term, this is also the foundation for unifying telemetry — if events are written as RDF triples into the store, `query sparql` becomes the single interface for debugging, analytics, and introspection." ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasUUID> "8e798316-ed1f-512c-91d3-d02eceb47c48" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Observability and Debugging Tools" ;
	a <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Charter> .
<urn:uuid:fbeed33b-787a-5702-aa16-37fd42a87478> a <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Charter> ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Parse Boundary and Mutation Safety" ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasUUID> "fbeed33b-787a-5702-aa16-37fd42a87478" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The parser currently has two behaviors (strict failure and recoverable parse), but command-level handling is inconsistent. This creates unsafe edges where partial recovery can silently become destructive file rewrites.\n\nThis charter defines a single parse boundary contract for the platform: syntax errors are systemic and block mutation; lint remains advisory for valid parses. It also defines observability hooks so parse health is measurable over time rather than inferred from incidents." ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasAlias> "parse_boundary" ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasCharterState> "Closed" .
<urn:uuid:344f2a0d-1a93-537a-b42b-a0cd1b6c7760> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasSubCharter> <urn:uuid:fbeed33b-787a-5702-aa16-37fd42a87478> .
<urn:uuid:fbeed33b-787a-5702-aa16-37fd42a87478> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000051> <urn:uuid:019db111-0001-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0002-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0003-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0004-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0005-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0006-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0007-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0008-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0009-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0010-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0011-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0012-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0013-7000-0000-000000000001> , <urn:uuid:019db111-0014-7000-0000-000000000001> .
<urn:uuid:019db111-0001-7000-0000-000000000001> a <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Action> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasUUID> "019db111-0001-7000-0000-000000000001" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "define parse boundary contract in core" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "explicit parse mode + outcome model landed in clearhead-core; syntax errors are systemic failures for mutation boundaries while lint remains advisory. legacy parse entry points remain available as wrappers over the new contract." ;
	<https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001868> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Completed> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasCompletedDateTime> "2026-04-21T13:40:00-07:00"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<urn:uuid:019db111-0002-7000-0000-000000000001> a <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Action> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasUUID> "019db111-0002-7000-0000-000000000001" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "add ParseMode and ParseOutcome types" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "strict/recover modes plus shared outcome payload (diagnostics + recovery metadata) are now exposed through the core parser seam." ;
	<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000050> <urn:uuid:019db111-0001-7000-0000-000000000001> ;
	<https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001868> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Completed> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasCompletedDateTime> "2026-04-21T13:40:00-07:00"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<urn:uuid:019db111-0003-7000-0000-000000000001> a <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Action> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasUUID> "019db111-0003-7000-0000-000000000001" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "add explicit ParseFailure diagnostic type" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "parse failures now carry explicit machine-readable structure so callers can enforce policy and present consistent failure output." ;
	<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000050> <urn:uuid:019db111-0001-7000-0000-000000000001> ;
	<https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001868> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Completed> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasCompletedDateTime> "2026-04-21T13:40:00-07:00"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<urn:uuid:019db111-0004-7000-0000-000000000001> a <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Action> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasUUID> "019db111-0004-7000-0000-000000000001" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "add parse contract tests in core" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "strict-vs-recover behavior is covered in core parser tests, including syntax failure and recovery semantics." ;
	<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000050> <urn:uuid:019db111-0001-7000-0000-000000000001> ;
	<https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001868> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Completed> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasCompletedDateTime> "2026-04-21T13:40:00-07:00"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<urn:uuid:019db111-0005-7000-0000-000000000001> a <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Action> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasUUID> "019db111-0005-7000-0000-000000000001" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "create CLI parse policy boundary for command handlers" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "read and mutation policies are centralized in commands/mod.rs helpers and now reused by plan, act, service, and file command paths. mutation paths block writes on parse failure." ;
	<https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001868> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Completed> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasCompletedDateTime> "2026-04-21T13:40:00-07:00"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<urn:uuid:019db111-0006-7000-0000-000000000001> a <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Action> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasUUID> "019db111-0006-7000-0000-000000000001" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "add load_actions_for_read helper" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "recover-mode read helper is now the shared entry point for file-based and content-based read paths with warning diagnostics." ;
	<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000050> <urn:uuid:019db111-0005-7000-0000-000000000001> ;
	<https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001868> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Completed> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasCompletedDateTime> "2026-04-21T13:40:00-07:00"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<urn:uuid:019db111-0007-7000-0000-000000000001> a <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Action> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasUUID> "019db111-0007-7000-0000-000000000001" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "add load_actions_for_mutation helper" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "mutation-safe loader and content parser enforce parse gating so malformed input never proceeds to write paths." ;
	<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000050> <urn:uuid:019db111-0005-7000-0000-000000000001> ;
	<https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001868> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Completed> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasCompletedDateTime> "2026-04-21T13:40:00-07:00"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<urn:uuid:019db111-0008-7000-0000-000000000001> a <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Action> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasUUID> "019db111-0008-7000-0000-000000000001" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "migrate expand acts to shared parse boundary" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "malformed files are skipped, healthy files continue, and overall command returns non-zero when any parse failures occur." ;
	<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000050> <urn:uuid:019db111-0005-7000-0000-000000000001> ;
	<https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001868> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Completed> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasCompletedDateTime> "2026-04-21T13:40:00-07:00"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<urn:uuid:019db111-0009-7000-0000-000000000001> a <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Action> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasUUID> "019db111-0009-7000-0000-000000000001" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "migrate plan mutating commands to shared parse boundary" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "add/update/complete/delete/archive all use mutation-safe loading and preserve non-destructive failure semantics." ;
	<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000050> <urn:uuid:019db111-0005-7000-0000-000000000001> ;
	<https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001868> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Completed> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasCompletedDateTime> "2026-04-21T13:40:00-07:00"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<urn:uuid:019db111-0010-7000-0000-000000000001> a <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Action> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasUUID> "019db111-0010-7000-0000-000000000001" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "wire parse boundary into observability pipeline" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "parse outcomes now emit consistent telemetry and user-facing diagnostics from shared command-boundary helpers." ;
	<https://www.commoncoreontologies.org/ont00001868> <https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#Completed> ;
	<https://clearhead.us/vocab/actions/v4#hasCompletedDateTime> "2026-04-21T13:40:00-07:00"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
