	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "add integration tests for non-destructive failure behavior" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "integration coverage now includes expand-acts safety plus additional read/export/sync/file command parse-boundary checks and mutation byte-stability assertions." ;
